references: Amending: Ord 58910. Repealing: Ord 62726. Related: CF 137938
summary: An ordinance relating to the Seattle Toll Bridge franchise granted by Ordinance No. 58910, extending the time for the commencement of construction of the toll bridge thereby contemplated; amending Section 5 of said Ordinance No. 58910, and repealing Ordinance No. 62726.
